SUMMARY:A Maze In Grace 20th Anniversary Re-Release Show with Sebastian St. James and Special Guests
DESCRIPTION:Sebastian St. James opens the night before the 8-piece Mitchell Thomas Band\, plus many special guests\, celebrate the release show for the 20th Anniversary of A Maze In Grace with a double-disc re-release including 18 bonus tracks. The band features Dave Sampson on guitar\, Kyle Turek on drums\, Ben Dubin on bass\, Faith Waligora on vocals\, Mingo Lewis Jr. on percussion\, Nick Hasty (Soul Glitch) on sax\, flute and keyboard\, and Evan Timmel on raps. Special guests include Bo Turek\, Matt Costa\, Katie Schuch\, and Christine Henry.
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/a-maze-in-grace-20th-anniversary-re-release-show-with-sebastian-st-james-and-special-guests/
LOCATION:The Big Easy\, 128 American Alley\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
CATEGORIES:Hip Hop,Jazz
END:VEVENT
