SUMMARY:Earthstart Organ Trio
DESCRIPTION:Earthstar Organ Trio creates saucy instrumental renditions of Pop\, R&B throwbacks and more with deep groove and fun arrangements. Featuring the soulful and daring guitar of Yishaia Hoffman\, the seductive keys and synth bass of Karl Rasmussen\, and the delicately thunderous grooves of Joeseph Carusi. Depending on the room they will chill on the groove or soar into shred town. The ever expanding setlist includes Stevie Wonder to Sam Smith. James Brown to Sade\, some great originals and more.
URL:https://bigeasypetaluma.com/event/earthstart-organ-trio/
